                    <span>People are either in love with this movie or completely hate it.  I'm somewhere in the middle as I had heard nothing but phenomenal reviews for it.  I was shocked at how much it wasn't a comedy and moreso a drama about two men trying to figure out 1)meaning of life 2) their place in it 3)neither one wanting to accept the realities of life.  I think people relate to this movie because they suffer the same three things above and somehow feel that this movie makes it that much better for them.  From an entertainment perspective it was ok at best.</span>
                  
